## 3. Text Legibility
- [ ] Minimum body font size ≥16px (WCAG Advisory)
- [ ] Line height ≥1.5× font size for body text
- [ ] Character line length: 45–75 characters per line
- [ ] Text not fully justified (causes uneven spacing for dyslexic readers)
- [ ] Text rendering: no all-caps body text longer than 3 words

## 4. Focus & Keyboard Navigation (for interactive deliverables)
- [ ] Focus indicator visible on all interactive elements (min 3:1 contrast against adjacent colors)
- [ ] Tab order logical and matches visual reading order
- [ ] No keyboard traps
- [ ] All actions achievable without mouse

